hildon-home (0.3.10) unstable; urgency=low

  * Open bookmark shortcuts in new browser window. Fixes: NB#97193
  * Add support for No-Window property in the notification groups
    configuration file. Use that option for the incoming-call and alarm-event
    category. Fixes: NB#98574
  * Fix memory leaks and a double-free discovered by Coverity.
  * Do not install default .schema file. Fixes: NB#101137, NB#96479, NB#96529

